{"id":285211,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/03/维权网-上海四名异议人士突然同时被传唤/","date":"2013-03-20T20:01:05Z","modified":"2013-03-20T20:01:05Z","title":"维权网 | 上海四名异议人士突然同时被传唤","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员华新报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>日傍晚</span><span>，上海四位异议人士李化平、杨勤恒、汪建华、高晓亮已经相约私下聚餐，但是在各自离家出发前，四人突然接到所住辖区派出所的电话传唤。传唤理由含含糊糊。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>四位被传唤的异议人士近期一直在推动上海同城公民每周聚餐活动，上周刚刚举行了第一次每周会餐，尽管受到很大阻挠，很多人被软禁在家中，仍然有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>多人举行公开会餐。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据了解，今晚四人突然被传唤，可能是上海国保试图阻止他们在一起商量筹备工作，因为他们已经计划本周末（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">23</span><span>日）继续举行开放式公民每周聚餐活动。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>目前高晓亮、汪建华、李化平等三位异议人士已经分别回到家中，但是杨勤恒仍然没有消息。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>高晓亮</span><span> </span><span>手机：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">135-2436-3793</span></div>\n<div><span>胡可师</span><span> </span><span>手机：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">138-1707-8071</span></div>\n<div><span>杨勤恒</span><span> </span><span>手机：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">131-6706-7718</span></div>\n<div><span>李化平</span><span> </span><span>手机：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">138-1610-7496</span></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18